M|Defe|**Im|md (keeps UI responsive during background tasks)**
M|Defe|tx|Use `requestIdleCallback()` to schedule non-ct work during browser idle periods. This keeps the main thread free for us interactions and animations, reducing jank and improving perceived perf.
M|Defe|**In|**
M|Defe|tx|```ts
M|Defe|func|string) {
M|Defe|tx|const results = searchItems(query)
M|Defe|tx|setResults(results)
M|Defe|tx|// These block the main thread immediately
M|Defe|tx|an.track('search', { query })
M|Defe|tx|saveToRecentSearches(query)
M|Defe|tx|prefetchTopResults(results.slice(0, 3))
M|Defe|tx|}
M|Defe|tx|```
M|Defe|**Co|**
M|Defe|tx|```ts
M|Defe|func|string) {
M|Defe|tx|const results = searchItems(query)
M|Defe|tx|setResults(results)
M|Defe|tx|// Defer non-ct work to idle periods
M|Defe|tx|requestIdleCallback(() => {
M|Defe|tx|an.track('search', { query })
M|Defe|tx|})
M|Defe|tx|requestIdleCallback(() => {
M|Defe|tx|saveToRecentSearches(query)
M|Defe|tx|})
M|Defe|tx|requestIdleCallback(() => {
M|Defe|tx|prefetchTopResults(results.slice(0, 3))
M|Defe|tx|})
M|Defe|tx|}
M|Defe|tx|```
